- MT2      : Elastic angular distribution                         4428 1451
                                                                  4428 1451
The flag LTT=3 is used to indicate a switch at some high energy,  4428 1451
generally 50 MeV, from a Legendre representation to a tabulated   4428 1451
representation. For incident energies below this energy, the      4428 1451
Legendre coefficients are given on a sufficiently precise energy  4428 1451
grid. They are a sum of calculated Legendre coefficients for      4428 1451
